Please book online at the Guy Savoy website: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.caesarspalace.com/restaurants/guy-savoy.html&quot;&gt;http://www.caesarspalace.com/restaurants/guy-savoy.html&lt;/a&gt; or contact Guy Savoy email at aalpe@caesarspalace.com to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell or local (hotel) phone number&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant Guy Savoy requires a credit card to hold your reservation. Your credit card will not be charged at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy- Cancellation Policy- You must cancel your reservation 24 hours prior to the dining date or a fee in the amount of $150 per person will be charged to the credit card on file&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Please contact the restaurant email to &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:aalpe@caesarspalace.com&quot;&gt;aalpe@caesarspalace.com&lt;/a&gt; 48 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm your dining reservation. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation&lt;/li&gt;
